---
layout: layouts/element.njk
title: "footer"
description: "Footer content for its nearest sectioning ancestor. Contains information about the author, copyright, related links, or metadata about the section."
elementName: footer
category: native
nativeGroup: Sectioning
currentPath: /docs/elements/native/footer/
permalink: /docs/elements/native/footer/
---

{% set defaultCode %}<footer>
  <p>Copyright 2024 Acme Corp. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>{% endset %}

{% set siteCode %}<footer class="site">
  <nav aria-label="Footer navigation">
    <ul class="inline">
      <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Privacy</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Terms</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
  <p><small>Copyright 2024 Vanilla Breeze.
  All rights reserved.</small></p>
</footer>{% endset %}

{% set articleCode %}<article>
  <h3>Article Title</h3>
  <p>Article content goes here...</p>
  <footer class="article">
    <p>Written by Jane Doe on
    <time datetime="2024-01-15">January 15, 2024</time></p>
    <p>Tags: HTML, CSS, Web Development</p>
  </footer>
</article>{% endset %}

{% set cardCode %}<layout-card>
  <header class="card">
    <h3>Card Title</h3>
  </header>
  <p>Card content with some description text.</p>
  <footer class="card">
    <button type="button">Action</button>
  </footer>
</layout-card>{% endset %}

{% set minimalCode %}<footer class="minimal">
  <p>Made with care by the Vanilla Breeze team</p>
</footer>{% endset %}

{% set columnsCode %}<footer class="columns">
  <section>
    <h4>Product</h4>
    <ul class="unstyled">
      <li><a href="#">Features</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Pricing</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Changelog</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section>
    <h4>Company</h4>
    <ul class="unstyled">
      <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Blog</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Careers</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section>
    <h4>Resources</h4>
    <ul class="unstyled">
      <li><a href="#">Documentation</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">API Reference</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Community</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section>
    <h4>Legal</h4>
    <ul class="unstyled">
      <li><a href="#">Privacy</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Terms</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Cookie Policy</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</footer>{% endset %}

  <section>
    <h2>Usage</h2>
    <p>Use the <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code> element for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Site-wide footer with navigation, copyright, and contact info</li>
      <li>Article footer with author info, tags, and share links</li>
      <li>Section footer with related content or actions</li>
      <li>Card footer with actions or metadata</li>
    </ul>
    <p>A page can have multiple footer elements: one for the document and additional ones within articles, sections, or other sectioning content.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Examples</h2>

    <h3>Default</h3>
    <p>Basic footer without additional styling.</p>
    <browser-window src="/docs/snippets/demos/footer-default.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/footer/default" title="Default footer" shadow></browser-window>
    <code-block language="html" label="Default footer">{{ defaultCode | escape }}</code-block>

    <h3>.site</h3>
    <p>Full-width site footer with raised background.</p>
    <browser-window src="/docs/snippets/demos/footer-site.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/footer/site" title="Site footer" shadow></browser-window>
    <code-block language="html" label="Site footer">{{ siteCode | escape }}</code-block>

    <h3>.article</h3>
    <p>Article footer with border and muted text.</p>
    <browser-window src="/docs/snippets/demos/footer-article.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/footer/article" title="Article footer" shadow></browser-window>
    <code-block language="html" label="Article footer">{{ articleCode | escape }}</code-block>

    <h3>.card</h3>
    <p>Card footer with border and raised background.</p>
    <browser-window src="/docs/snippets/demos/footer-card.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/footer/card" title="Card footer" shadow></browser-window>
    <code-block language="html" label="Card footer">{{ cardCode | escape }}</code-block>

    <h3>.minimal</h3>
    <p>Simple centered footer with small text.</p>
    <browser-window src="/docs/snippets/demos/footer-minimal.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/footer/minimal" title="Minimal footer" shadow></browser-window>
    <code-block language="html" label="Minimal footer">{{ minimalCode | escape }}</code-block>

    <h3>.columns</h3>
    <p>Multi-column footer layout for site footers.</p>
    <browser-window src="/docs/snippets/demos/footer-columns.html" url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/footer/columns" title="Column footer" shadow></browser-window>
    <code-block language="html" label="Column footer">{{ columnsCode | escape }}</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Variants</h2>
    <table class="props-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Class</th>
          <th>Description</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><code>.site</code></td>
          <td>Full-width with generous padding and raised background</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><code>.article</code></td>
          <td>Top border with muted, smaller text for article metadata</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><code>.card</code></td>
          <td>Top border with raised background for card actions</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><code>.minimal</code></td>
          <td>Centered, small, muted text for simple footers</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><code>.columns</code></td>
          <td>Auto-fit grid layout for multi-column site footers</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><code>.sticky</code></td>
          <td>Sticks to bottom with background and top border</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Accessibility</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>The document's main footer becomes a contentinfo landmark (only when not nested)</li>
      <li>Include skip links to bypass footer navigation when appropriate</li>
      <li>Use <code>&lt;nav&gt;</code> with <code>aria-label="Footer navigation"</code> for footer nav sections</li>
      <li>Ensure sufficient color contrast for muted footer text</li>
      <li>Footer links should be keyboard accessible and have visible focus states</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Related Elements</h2>
